{"tid":2350422,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"windows 無限自動修復","createTime":"2021-01-02T09:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T03:33:47.000Z","uid":195899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0633be39b27c1fb4ee76364fca2dcc22b36fd05","tid":2350422,"uid":195899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"更新windows 10 20版後，唔知係咪撞nvme，經常重啟，但開到機。<br />\n可以入藍畫面重裝windows及燒機，仍會自動重啟，確認硬件無問題。<br />\n<br />\n有日入藍畫面，回到原始點及解除更新，整完出事<br />\n1.無限自動修復<br />\n2.無咗系統管理員身份，無得入命令/回原始點/重裝windows<br />\n3.重設windows失敗<br />\n4.安全模式都會自動修復<br />\n5.入到uefi <br />\n<br />\n依家咁樣，係咪只可以入uefi 重裝windows。<br />\n<br />\n重裝/還原要系統管理員，而管理員身份又自動消失咗，要開到機先可以整返，但開到機仲洗鬼係藍畫面重裝咩"},{"pid":"681382bb473067f30ac651216407c3c8296ede4c","tid":2350422,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:21:17.000Z","msg":"linux"},{"pid":"8b3d49cfbaa5389c7eff5347386bcdceaf3fbcb5","tid":2350422,"uid":92017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"681382bb473067f30ac651216407c3c8296ede4c","tid":2350422,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:21:17.000Z","msg":"linux"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37c48e4dcbe2e793ae911cc11fa6daa2b26aef1","tid":2350422,"uid":387307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:02:16.000Z","msg":"用USB果隻重裝都要系統管理員???"},{"pid":"11b8d0221c83eaaf3c2cf102783e50eeaeb79497","tid":2350422,"uid":195899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e37c48e4dcbe2e793ae911cc11fa6daa2b26aef1","tid":2350422,"uid":387307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:02:16.000Z","msg":"用USB果隻重裝都要系統管理員???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"呢招未試，我諗住等佢出更新，解決咗nvme問題先再重裝。<br />\n不過，又好似唔多覺有人報windows更新完撞nvme."},{"pid":"7e8b449c1b8662776d7dd0be3bf86aa6ce5ad5a0","tid":2350422,"uid":195899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:46:38.000Z","msg":"暫時解決咗，插左隻windows 10手指，又可以入到還原，還原完開到機。<br />\n插隻手指=有返管理員身份，好奇怪.<br />\n依家睇下仲會唔會撞nvme，windows 官網寫11月解決咗，但我12月都仲係不斷重啟，檢查晒其他野無問題。"},{"pid":"2590285f4f7a987f22715717de57fb21b07b69a8","tid":2350422,"uid":387307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8b449c1b8662776d7dd0be3bf86aa6ce5ad5a0","tid":2350422,"uid":195899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:46:38.000Z","msg":"暫時解決咗，插左隻windows 10手指，又可以入到還原，還原完開到機。<br />\n插隻手指=有返管理員身份，好奇怪.<br />\n依家睇下仲會唔會撞nvme，windows 官網寫11月解決咗，但我12月都仲係不斷重啟，檢查晒其他野無問題。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T03:33:47.000Z","msg":"唔係插隻手指就等於有管理員權限<br />\n係重裝本來就應該用碟OR手指<br />\n咩都唔用果種只係叫RESET"}]}